25
00:03:12,420 --> 00:03:14,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What does Norabo mean?</font>

26
00:03:14,630 --> 00:03:18,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a vegetable where I 
grew up called Norabo leaves.</font>

27
00:03:18,750 --> 00:03:22,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, what do you want from me?</font>

28
00:03:24,140 --> 00:03:28,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a trainee at our school 
named Hanazawa Yuusaku.</font>

29
00:03:29,310 --> 00:03:32,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The son of Division Commander Hanazawa,</font>

30
00:03:32,140 --> 00:03:33,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who runs the 7th Division in Hokkaido.</font>

31
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:37,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want you to pretend to be him 
for an arranged marriage meeting.</font>

32
00:03:38,600 --> 00:03:39,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pretend to be him?</font>

33
00:03:40,120 --> 00:03:44,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Commander Hanazawa wants his son 
to be a regimental flag bearer.</font>

34
00:03:45,100 --> 00:03:47,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But his wife, Hanazawa Hiro,</font>

35
00:03:47,660 --> 00:03:51,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">doesn't want her son doing a job 
with such a high casualty rate.</font>

36
00:03:51,740 --> 00:03:55,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But she's the wife of a soldier 
and could never say so.</font>

37
00:03:56,370 --> 00:04:01,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She secretly contacted a place called 
the Tokyo Marriage Matchmakers.</font>

38
00:04:01,480 --> 00:04:04,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She says it's common for 
young kids these days</font>

39
00:04:04,130 --> 00:04:07,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to register there and have arranged 
marriage meetings without their parents.</font>

40
00:04:09,370 --> 00:04:12,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's got her eyes on 
a certain girl there.</font>

41
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:15,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Her name is Kaneko Kaeko.</font>

42
00:04:15,290 --> 00:04:17,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Her parents are important directors 
in the Mitsubishi zaibatsu,</font>

43
00:04:17,530 --> 00:04:20,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and she's attending a fancy girls' school.</font>

44
00:04:20,360 --> 00:04:24,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At the school you leave as soon 
as you're engaged to be married.</font>

45
00:04:24,420 --> 00:04:28,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you can't get married by the time you 
graduate you're treated like leftovers.</font>

46
00:04:29,050 --> 00:04:33,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kaneko Kaeko is panicking 
because no one will marry her.</font>

47
00:04:33,590 --> 00:04:35,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even though she's rich?</font>

48
00:04:35,820 --> 00:04:40,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All the prospective candidates are 
rich. They don't care about that.</font>

49
00:04:40,970 --> 00:04:43,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But she's pretty.</font>

50
00:04:43,390 --> 00:04:47,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone looks way prettier 
than they are in these photos.</font>

51
00:04:47,200 --> 00:04:50,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When you see her for real, her nasty 
personality shows in her face.</font>

52
00:04:50,970 --> 00:04:54,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hanazawa's mother's letters to Kaneko</font>

53
00:04:54,210 --> 00:04:58,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">include instructions to 
"steal Yuusaku-san's virginity."</font>

54
