58
00:05:09,740 --> 00:05:13,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and pull him out of the military 
and into the zaibatsu.</font>

59
00:05:13,650 --> 00:05:18,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Commander Hanazawa found 
out what his wife is up to.</font>

60
00:05:18,500 --> 00:05:20,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's far away in Hokkaido,</font>

61
00:05:20,690 --> 00:05:23,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so he asked the 1st Division Commander, 
a man he can trust, for help.</font>

62
00:05:23,900 --> 00:05:26,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And now he's asked me to deal with it.</font>

63
00:05:27,010 --> 00:05:29,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no need to go 
through all those hoops.</font>

64
00:05:29,070 --> 00:05:32,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His wife's right next to him. 
She can just talk to him.</font>

65
00:05:32,590 --> 00:05:33,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ideally, yes.</font>

66
00:05:34,290 --> 00:05:39,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But she's already crossed the line 
and involved other people in this.</font>

67
00:05:40,250 --> 00:05:43,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This could turn into a problem 
that affects the morale of</font>

68
00:05:43,930 --> 00:05:45,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the whole 7th Division.</font>

69
00:05:45,470 --> 00:05:46,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The wife of their Division Commander</font>

70
