<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. Don't get them messy.</font>

74
00:06:03,460 --> 00:06:06,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There must be any number of people 
at the academy you could ask.</font>

75
00:06:06,820 --> 00:06:08,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why me?</font>

76
00:06:08,710 --> 00:06:10,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Idiot.</font>

77
00:06:10,020 --> 00:06:15,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I use someone from the school, rumors 
about the Hanazawa lady will spread.</font>

78
00:06:14,930 --> 00:06:17,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Here, put on the hat, too.</font>

79
00:06:22,400 --> 00:06:23,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

80
