<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hah!</font>

102
00:07:28,130 --> 00:07:31,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay! There's nothing left to teach you!</font>

103
00:07:31,390 --> 00:07:34,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Begin Operation 
"Defend Hanazawa Yuusaku's Virginity!"</font>

104
