<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm?</font>

106
00:07:48,070 --> 00:07:49,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No! No! She'll find out!</font>

107
00:07:49,770 --> 00:07:51,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's about to find out already!</font>

108
00:07:52,010 --> 00:07:54,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Kikuta-san! The mission's in danger!</i></font>

109
00:07:56,070 --> 00:08:01,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's about to give the 
"mission failed" signal already!</font>

110
00:08:04,440 --> 00:08:06,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Yuusaku-san...</font>

111
00:08:07,880 --> 00:08:10,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I imagined you as someone more stern.</font>

112
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:15,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanted to lighten the mood.</font>

113
00:08:15,490 --> 00:08:19,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you still have your hat 
on because you're nervous?</font>

114
00:08:22,270 --> 00:08:26,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I always eat Japanese food, 
both at home and at the academy.</font>

115
00:08:26,640 --> 00:08:28,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I'm not used to places like this.</font>

116
00:08:30,350 --> 00:08:33,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You look so different in person.</font>

117
00:08:34,190 --> 00:08:35,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

118
00:08:37,390 --> 00:08:40,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you've never had fried shrimp, then?</font>

119
00:08:40,100 --> 00:08:42,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're a popular dish lately.</font>

120
00:08:42,710 --> 00:08:46,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're delicious with egg sauce.</font>

121
00:08:49,830 --> 00:08:51,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wow!</i></font>

122
00:08:51,450 --> 00:08:53,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've never had anything like this.</i></font>

123
00:08:54,290 --> 00:08:56,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you come here often?</font>

124
00:08:56,390 --> 00:08:57,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

125
00:08:57,250 --> 00:08:59,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And also the Rokumeikan.</font>

126
00:08:59,610 --> 00:09:04,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My friends at school are all daughters 
of the royal family, ministers,</font>

127
00:09:04,430 --> 00:09:06,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">important officials or governors.</font>

128
00:09:06,660 --> 00:09:08,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So we have to go somewhere nice.</font>

129
00:09:09,410 --> 00:09:14,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Since my dad died, I had to 
steal food from people's cats.</i></font>

130
00:09:21,190 --> 00:09:22,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How'd it go?</font>

131
00:09:22,940 --> 00:09:25,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't talk much about myself.</font>

132
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:27,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I tried to pretend to be someone boring.</font>

133
00:09:27,240 --> 00:09:29,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good, good. Excellent work, Norabo.</font>

134
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:33,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Arranged marriages like this one involve 
at least two or three meetings.</font>

135
00:09:33,640 --> 00:09:34,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So get ready for the next one.</font>

136
00:09:35,820 --> 00:09:40,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was so quiet. He just nodded 
and never corrected me.</font>

137
00:09:40,260 --> 00:09:42,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really liked him!</font>

138
00:09:42,590 --> 00:09:44,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And more than anything...</font>

139
00:09:44,310 --> 00:09:46,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was hot!</font>

140
00:09:46,220 --> 00:09:49,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You do prefer good-looking men.</font>

141
