<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why you're not married yet.</font>

142
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:56,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't imagine marrying someone 
you've only met a few times.</font>

143
00:09:56,820 --> 00:10:00,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's how it works. 
Particularly for the upper classes.</font>

144
00:10:00,920 --> 00:10:03,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure everybody would 
rather marry someone they liked,</font>

145
00:10:04,280 --> 00:10:06,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but they don't get a choice.</font>

146
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:13,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

147
00:10:13,480 --> 00:10:17,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have friends back home 
named Ume-chan and Toraji.</font>

148
00:10:18,540 --> 00:10:21,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was supposed to marry Ume-chan.</font>

149
00:10:21,890 --> 00:10:24,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But someone in my family got tuberculosis.</font>

150
00:10:25,890 --> 00:10:28,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then everyone in 
my family died from it.</font>

151
00:10:34,380 --> 00:10:36,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want to kill you, Ume-chan!</font>

152
00:10:37,930 --> 00:10:39,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I said that if two years 
passed and I didn't get sick,</font>

153
00:10:39,780 --> 00:10:40,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd go back to the village.</font>

154
00:10:41,660 --> 00:10:43,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That I'd come for her.</font>

155
00:10:49,150 --> 00:10:50,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She married Toraji.</font>

156
00:10:51,830 --> 00:10:55,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He'd loved Ume-chan since they were young.</font>

157
00:10:56,900 --> 00:10:57,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So...</font>

158
00:10:58,790 --> 00:11:00,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did you come back?</font>

159
00:11:00,820 --> 00:11:03,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She still cares about you...</font>

160
00:11:03,110 --> 00:11:06,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But she's my wife anyway!</font>

161
00:11:09,610 --> 00:11:12,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Congratulations on your marriage, Toraji.</font>

162
00:11:13,010 --> 00:11:16,530
