166
00:11:25,070 --> 00:11:28,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but you don't know if she's really happy?</font>

167
00:11:28,480 --> 00:11:31,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the fuck do you know about 
Ume-chan, you little brat?!</font>

168
00:11:31,340 --> 00:11:32,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, uh...</font>

169
00:11:32,540 --> 00:11:37,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't get so damn cocky just because 
you're kind of handsome, you fucking kid!</font>

170
00:11:37,800 --> 00:11:40,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gah, you're pissing me off!</font>

171
00:11:40,340 --> 00:11:45,590
