176
00:11:54,480 --> 00:11:57,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Face it and apologize, damn it!</font>

177
00:11:58,360 --> 00:12:00,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Am I just hanging on to 
