178
00:12:01,580 --> 00:12:02,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it's fine.</font>

179
00:12:02,550 --> 00:12:03,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

180
00:12:03,020 --> 00:12:05,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Men are pathetic creatures.</font>

181
00:12:05,250 --> 00:12:08,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's okay to keep the woman 
