182
00:12:08,290 --> 00:12:10,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and remember her once in a while.</font>

183
00:12:11,210 --> 00:12:15,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that's why if you're a man, 
you should understand Toraji's fears.</font>

184
00:12:15,400 --> 00:12:18,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forget your home and both of them.</font>

185
00:12:19,650 --> 00:12:20,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir.</font>

186
00:12:21,570 --> 00:12:26,010
<font size="40"><b><font color="#f5f5f1">Golden Kamuy</font></b></font>

187
00:12:26,470 --> 00:12:28,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've decided! I'm marrying Yuusaku-san!</font>

188
00:12:28,710 --> 00:12:30,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not giving up on him.</font>

189
00:12:30,680 --> 00:12:35,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Men are easy. Just make it 
look like you'll fuck them.</font>

190
00:12:35,020 --> 00:12:36,530
