<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">wrap your legs around them 
and make them scream.</font>

192
00:12:38,990 --> 00:12:41,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yuusaku-san's from an important family,</font>

193
00:12:41,740 --> 00:12:44,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and men choose based on looks, right?</font>

194
00:12:44,780 --> 00:12:46,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I'll do the same thing!</font>

195
00:12:47,340 --> 00:12:51,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My cousin says I put too 
much importance on looks.</font>

196
00:12:51,700 --> 00:12:56,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But he did the same thing, 
and he seems happy.</font>

197
00:12:56,110 --> 00:12:59,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That country girl with curly hair...</font>

198
00:13:01,350 --> 00:13:03,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That fried shrimp was good.</font>

199
00:13:03,860 --> 00:13:06,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tokyo's got good food
if you can pay for it.</font>

200
00:13:06,920 --> 00:13:08,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've got to get rich first.</font>

201
00:13:08,530 --> 00:13:12,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does Hanazawa Yuusaku want 
to be a flag-bearer, anyway?</font>

202
00:13:14,530 --> 00:13:16,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe he wants to eat</font>

203
00:13:16,050 --> 00:13:19,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">fried shrimp at the Imperial Hotel 
instead of going into the army.</font>

204
00:13:19,850 --> 00:13:22,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't need to think about any of that.</font>

205
00:13:23,250 --> 00:13:28,070
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#0f1122">Cafeteria</font></b></font>

206
00:13:25,010 --> 00:13:28,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this operation really going to work?</font>

207
00:13:29,090 --> 00:13:30,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not confident.</font>

208
00:13:30,750 --> 00:13:33,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keep the uniform. And the hat.</font>

209
00:13:34,100 --> 00:13:36,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They'll give you strength.</font>

210
00:13:36,920 --> 00:13:40,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A thing contains a part 
of its owner's power.</font>

211
00:13:40,920 --> 00:13:43,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you wear what someone else wore,</font>

212
00:13:43,470 --> 00:13:45,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you'll get a bit of their strength.</font>

213
00:13:46,100 --> 00:13:48,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are those the words of a famous monk?</font>

214
00:13:48,490 --> 00:13:50,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what I believe.</font>

215
00:13:50,570 --> 00:13:54,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">During the Sino-Japanese War, I carried 
the things of my comrades and enemies.</font>

216
00:13:54,680 --> 00:13:56,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On the battlefield,</font>

217
00:13:56,330 --> 00:13:59,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you need something to keep your 
spirits up more than anything.</font>

218
00:14:00,890 --> 00:14:03,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But don't wander around 
in that uniform, okay?</font>

219
00:14:03,660 --> 00:14:05,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Akasaka is army territory.</font>

220
00:14:05,950 --> 00:14:09,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The academy, and the students 
you fought with, are nearby.</font>

221
00:14:09,390 --> 00:14:11,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No getting into fights.</font>

222
00:14:11,200 --> 00:14:13,160
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b><font color="#4c4943"><font size="25">Army Officer Academy</font></font></b></font>

223
00:14:14,890 --> 00:14:17,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you the one who wanted to talk to me?</font>

224
00:14:17,850 --> 00:14:19,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you Hanazawa Yuusaku-san?</font>

225
00:14:19,650 --> 00:14:21,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have we met?</font>

226
00:14:21,410 --> 00:14:23,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What company and unit are you in?</font>

227
00:14:23,940 --> 00:14:24,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's your name?</font>

228
00:14:25,230 --> 00:14:28,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry. This won't take long.</font>

229
00:14:29,050 --> 00:14:33,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it true that your father wants 
you to be a regimental flag-bearer?</font>

230
00:14:33,560 --> 00:14:35,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Yes.</font>

231
00:14:35,690 --> 00:14:38,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'd have to be chosen first.</font>

232
00:14:38,710 --> 00:14:40,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who told you that?</font>

233
00:14:40,550 --> 00:14:42,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's it to you?</font>

234
00:14:42,390 --> 00:14:46,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why does he want his son to take a 
job that's likely to get him killed?</font>

235
00:14:46,780 --> 00:14:49,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is he just that confident 
there won't be a war?</font>

236
00:14:50,390 --> 00:14:52,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not true.</font>

237
00:14:52,420 --> 00:14:54,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Russia has already invaded Manchuria.</font>

238
00:14:54,970 --> 00:15:00,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My father says that war is coming 
soon, and so it probably is.</font>

239
00:15:00,740 --> 00:15:02,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you want to be a flag-bearer?</font>

240
00:15:03,180 --> 00:15:05,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd be proud if I was chosen.</font>

241
00:15:05,220 --> 00:15:06,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not because that's 
what your father wants?</font>

242
00:15:07,220 --> 00:15:08,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not true.</font>

243
00:15:09,330 --> 00:15:10,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you trying to say?</font>

244
00:15:10,850 --> 00:15:12,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did you ask me to come here?</font>

245
00:15:13,300 --> 00:15:16,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to know what you really think.</font>

246
00:15:16,510 --> 00:15:21,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My father's always told me to think 
about what I can do for Japan.</font>

247
00:15:21,930 --> 00:15:24,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I understand why he feels that way.</font>

248
00:15:24,310 --> 00:15:28,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And if I can help raise the spirits 
of the soldiers on the front lines...</font>

249
00:15:28,440 --> 00:15:29,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't bullshit me!</font>

250
00:15:31,330 --> 00:15:34,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What you really want is fried 
shrimp, isn't it, you asshole?</font>

251
00:15:34,420 --> 00:15:36,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fried shrimp? What are you talking about?</font>

252
00:15:37,350 --> 00:15:38,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ow... ow...</font>

253
00:15:38,660 --> 00:15:40,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't know what it is?</font>

254
00:15:40,900 --> 00:15:43,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then go try it at the Imperial Hotel!</font>

255
00:15:43,900 --> 00:15:46,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then you can choose!</font>

256
00:15:46,030 --> 00:15:47,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you saying?</font>

257
00:15:47,630 --> 00:15:49,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This man's crazy!</font>

258
00:15:49,790 --> 00:15:50,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Somebody help...</font>

259
00:15:51,870 --> 00:15:54,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that Sergeant Kikuta's hat?</font>

260
00:15:57,180 --> 00:15:59,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That small stitch...</font>

261
00:15:59,410 --> 00:16:01,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's from a hole that was made</font>

262
00:16:01,310 --> 00:16:05,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">when a trainee almost killed 
him during firing practice.</font>

263
00:16:05,710 --> 00:16:07,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shit. I'd better run.</font>

264
00:16:08,170 --> 00:16:10,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was a gift. I'll be on my way.</font>

265
00:16:10,400 --> 00:16:11,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Farewell.</font>

266
00:16:11,670 --> 00:16:12,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A gift?</font>

267
00:16:13,080 --> 00:16:17,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That hat belonged to his younger brother, 
who died during the Sino-Japanese war.</font>

268
00:16:36,760 --> 00:16:37,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

269
00:16:39,950 --> 00:16:42,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There really are a lot of soldiers here.</i></font>

270
00:16:43,390 --> 00:16:46,900
<font face="Times New Roman" size="24"><b>Army First Division Command</b></font>

271
00:16:48,860 --> 00:16:53,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ainu gold? Is that true?</font>

272
00:16:53,280 --> 00:16:54,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes!</font>

273
00:16:54,370 --> 00:16:57,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want you to find it for 
the central government.</font>

274
00:16:57,700 --> 00:17:02,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Your reputation at intelligence 
gathering is unparalleled.</font>

275
00:16:58,340 --> 00:17:03,060
<font face="Times New Roman" size="24"><b><font size="14">Army First Division Commander
<font size="24"> General Okuda Hidenobu</font></font></b></font>

276
00:17:02,450 --> 00:17:05,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want you to keep me informed 
of your progress at all times.</font>

277
00:17:05,330 --> 00:17:08,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And go above the heads 
of my superior officers?</font>

278
00:17:08,930 --> 00:17:10,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Correct.</font>

279
00:17:10,390 --> 00:17:13,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry. I'll back you up.</font>

280
00:17:13,480 --> 00:17:16,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seventh Division Commander 
Hanazawa-dono owes me a debt.</font>

281
00:17:16,950 --> 00:17:19,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll be able to move freely.</font>

282
00:17:19,220 --> 00:17:21,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A debt?</font>

283
00:17:21,310 --> 00:17:24,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I covered up an embarrassing 
incident with his family.</font>

284
00:17:24,320 --> 00:17:27,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's from Satsuma, and 
given the struggles between</font>

285
00:17:27,950 --> 00:17:30,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">factions in Satsuma and Choushuu,</font>

286
00:17:30,390 --> 00:17:32,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he wouldn't want a 
scandal coming to light.</font>

287
00:17:33,320 --> 00:17:37,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He assumed that as I am from
Kokura Province, I'd be neutral,</font>

288
00:17:37,840 --> 00:17:39,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so he came to me.</font>

289
00:17:39,800 --> 00:17:41,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He showed me his weakness.</font>

290
00:17:42,760 --> 00:17:45,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lieutenant Tsurumi, you're from Niigata, yes?</font>

291
00:17:45,710 --> 00:17:49,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your family were important 
nobles in Echigo Nagaoka,</font>

292
00:17:49,100 --> 00:17:52,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who met with a terrible fate 
during the Battle of Hokuetsu.</font>

293
00:17:52,940 --> 00:17:55,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You hate both Choushuu and Satsuma, right?</font>

294
00:17:55,770 --> 00:18:00,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's use the Ainu gold to put an 
end to their rule over the army.</font>

295
00:18:02,120 --> 00:18:07,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I ask you to tell me 
more about this "scandal"?</font>

296
00:18:07,730 --> 00:18:12,230
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b><font size="8"><font color="#503d2d">Army First Division Headquarters</font></font></b></font>

297
00:18:08,510 --> 00:18:12,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're not from Satsuma or 
Choushuu, you're not a real soldier!</font>

298
00:18:12,480 --> 00:18:15,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what our nation's 
army and navy say.</font>

299
00:18:16,610 --> 00:18:19,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">General Okuta said he was neutral.</font>

300
00:18:19,780 --> 00:18:21,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But he's lying.</font>

301
00:18:21,210 --> 00:18:23,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's actually with Choushuu, I assume.</font>

302
00:18:24,250 --> 00:18:27,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's afraid that if the Ainu 
gold ends up in his hands,</font>

303
00:18:27,520 --> 00:18:30,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the Satsuma faction will get stronger.</font>

304
00:18:30,960 --> 00:18:34,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How stupid it all is!</font>

305
00:18:34,130 --> 00:18:36,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sick of the central government.</font>

306
00:18:37,690 --> 00:18:39,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, it's fine.</font>

307
00:18:39,170 --> 00:18:42,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I found information on 
the Ainu gold in Russia.</font>

308
00:18:42,670 --> 00:18:44,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And this confirms it.</font>

309
00:18:44,710 --> 00:18:50,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Before we return to Hokkaido, we'll 
need to meet Commander Hanazawa's son.</font>

310
00:18:50,920 --> 00:18:53,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And this sergeant named Kikuta, too.</font>

311
00:18:54,610 --> 00:18:58,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The lady contacted Hanazawa 
Yuusaku at the academy.</font>

312
00:18:58,850 --> 00:19:01,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She asked to meet at the 
Imperial Hotel again.</font>

313
00:19:01,560 --> 00:19:03,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What if she finds out?</font>

314
00:19:04,070 --> 00:19:07,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You give back the uniform, 
and you're done.</font>

315
00:19:07,500 --> 00:19:11,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, not me. What about the lady?</font>

316
00:19:11,090 --> 00:19:14,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She knows about an army scandal, right?</font>

317
00:19:15,910 --> 00:19:18,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course, we have a backup plan.</font>

318
00:19:18,900 --> 00:19:21,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But there's no need for you to know it.</font>

319
00:19:22,340 --> 00:19:24,300
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b><font color="#4c4943"><font size="25">Army Officer Academy</font></font></b></font>

320
00:19:23,500 --> 00:19:28,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hanazawa-san, did you get the 
information from Sergeant Kikuta?</font>

321
00:19:28,340 --> 00:19:30,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's supposed to be today.</font>

322
00:19:30,230 --> 00:19:32,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking about?</font>

323
00:19:32,720 --> 00:19:34,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">About the Imperial Hotel.</font>

324
00:19:34,970 --> 00:19:35,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you not hear?</font>

325
00:19:35,880 --> 00:19:36,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Suzuki-san!</font>

326
00:19:36,960 --> 00:19:38,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not supposed to tell him!</font>

327
00:19:40,200 --> 00:19:45,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All telegrams and letters to me 
are to go through Sergeant Kikuta?!</font>

328
00:19:45,250 --> 00:19:47,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, that was the order.</font>

329
00:19:54,180 --> 00:19:58,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hanazawa Yuusaku-kun? You just missed him.</font>

330
00:19:58,370 --> 00:19:59,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where did he go?</font>

331
00:20:09,310 --> 00:20:11,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so sorry!</font>

332
00:20:11,730 --> 00:20:13,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, man...</font>

333
00:20:13,140 --> 00:20:18,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no! Yuusaku-san is 
covered in beef stew!</font>

334
00:20:19,110 --> 00:20:20,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come this way...</font>

335
00:20:20,750 --> 00:20:22,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll help you change.</font>

336
00:20:22,560 --> 00:20:23,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Change?</font>

337
00:20:24,730 --> 00:20:26,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where are they going?</font>

338
00:20:26,500 --> 00:20:29,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've got us a room.</font>

339
00:20:29,780 --> 00:20:31,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A room?</font>

340
00:20:31,830 --> 00:20:33,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lieutenant Tsurumi...</font>

341
00:20:36,530 --> 00:20:38,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a bath in the back.</font>

342
00:20:38,790 --> 00:20:40,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take it all off!</font>

343
00:20:40,740 --> 00:20:42,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All off! Strip!</font>

344
00:20:42,440 --> 00:20:43,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Strip?</font>

345
00:20:45,130 --> 00:20:46,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This room is crazy...</font>

